    "en": {
      "title": "Chatham Street heats up",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tens of thousands of people have gathered and protested on the road leading to the President's House and a very hot situation has been created in Chatham Street.",
        "Despite firing two rounds of tear gas, the security forces could not control the crowd. According to this, several shots were fired in the air in order to control the crowd.",
        "It is also reported that two more roadblocks have been added to the road leading to the Presidential Palace."
      ],
